<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Travel Diary</title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: aliceblue;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Text Shadow */
    h1 {
      color: navy;
      text-shadow: 3px 3px 5px gray;
    }

    /* Box Shadow */
    .diary-card {
      width: 400px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 5px 5px 12px gray;
    }

    /* Text Indent */
    .story {
      text-indent: 40px;
      text-align: left;
      color: darkslategray;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .footer {
      color: darkblue;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>My Travel Diary</h1>

  <div class="diary-card">
    <p class="story">
      Last summer, I visited a beautiful hill station surrounded by green forests and waterfalls.
      The fresh air, peaceful environment, and scenic views made the trip unforgettable.
      I enjoyed hiking, taking photographs, and exploring local culture.
    </p>

    <p class="footer">Written by ___________</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
